er.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) is on offer at Bonhams with an estima=
te of $180,000. In 2007, a similar image in almost the same size was sold f=
or $481,000 at auction. The current estimate is a big step back, part of th=
e retreat I=E2=80=99ve been trying to describe. But it=E2=80=99s also an en=
ticement which could
draw some of the attention on Estes back to Goings if it sells really well.

Also at Bonhams is a painting ( https://www.bonhams.com/auction/30364/lot/1=
24/john-kacere-1920-1999-joelle-89-39-78-x-60-14-in-1012-x-1531-cm-painted-=
