 all clear why Artnet believes an issue with auditors was reason enough to =
cancel its shareholder meeting, let alone days before the event. Even if yo=
u believe Artnet=E2=80=99s version of events, the auditors quit three weeks=
 ago. Why not inform shareholders right away, allowing them time to cancel =
plans to travel to Berlin? <br/><br/>Weng made clear in a statement last Th=
ursday that he, too, was annoyed by the delay, describing the cancellation =
